Package: ppcheck
Type: Package
Title: Graphical Posterior Predictive Checks for Bayesian Models
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2016-06-05
Authors@R: c(person("Jonah", "Gabry", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jsg2201@columbia.edu"),
             person("Paul-Christian", "Buerkner", role = "ctb"))
Maintainer: Jonah Gabry <jsg2201@columbia.edu>
Description: Functions for creating graphical displays comparing observed data to simulated data from the posterior predictive distribution after fitting Bayesian models.
